{
     "hosting": {
         // ...other configuration...  
       	"public":"dist",//specify the path for public folder (relative)   
       }     
}
 ```
This will ensure that your static files are served from memory and can be accessed at http://localhost:3000/.  If you're deploying on Vercel, it should default to '/'.  
